org.openbel.framework.core.kam
Interface KAMLoader

All Known Implementing Classes:
JdbcKAMLoaderImpl
public interface KAMLoader

KamLoader defines a database loader to load a KAM into the KAMstore schema.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>

Loads the global KAM nodes into the KAM including the parameter and term objects.

Parameters:
nt - NamespaceTable, the namespace table where the parameter's namespaces are associated
pt - ParameterTable, the parameter table where the parameters are stored

Throws:
SQLException - - Thrown if a SQL error occurred while loading the parameters.
